{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311211, "create_time": 1658674620, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "可怜的吴啊萍", "timestamp": 1658674620}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311215, "create_time": 1658674703, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "u1s1，感觉确实挺离谱的。。。", "timestamp": 1658674703}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311216, "create_time": 1658674721, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "而且留的还是真名，感觉可能真是心理出问题了", "timestamp": 1658674721}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311223, "create_time": 1658674804, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "本来遭受噩梦缠身，想求助于佛，结果还要无端遭受牢狱之灾。佛教（大乘）本就倡导度化众生，哪里违背了佛教的理念呢。", "timestamp": 1658674804}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311239, "create_time": 1658675086, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "这…", "timestamp": 1658675086}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311240, "create_time": 1658675118, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "真的不知道该如何说是好…", "timestamp": 1658675118}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311260, "create_time": 1658675392, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "我麻了，这居然也是犯罪...寻衅滋事可太牛逼了", "timestamp": 1658675392}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311330, "create_time": 1658676127, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "额作为一个对佛教有点感兴趣的非佛教徒，感觉还挺理解她的，当然肯定有点不正常就是了", "timestamp": 1658676127}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311336, "create_time": 1658676221, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "帮助战犯解脱苦难可太牛逼了", "timestamp": 1658676221}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311341, "create_time": 1658676246, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "佛教并没有什么“惩恶扬善”的教义，只有普度众生的教义", "timestamp": 1658676246}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311351, "create_time": 1658676299, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Eve: 佛教就是这样的，普度众生，慈悲为怀", "timestamp": 1658676299}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311365, "create_time": 1658676431, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 就佛教体系而言，战犯犯了如此大的罪，当然他们受到的因果报应也就更大。而帮助众生解脱其实也是菩萨的行为，所以就原理而言是没问题的。", "timestamp": 1658676431}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311399, "create_time": 1658676775, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 在佛教体系里，惩罚战犯的是因果而不是人，所以人没必要再关心如何惩罚已经转世轮回的战犯了，他们已经受到了该受的报应。", "timestamp": 1658676775}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311430, "create_time": 1658677448, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "所谓帮助众生解脱，无论是供奉还是讲经，本质都是让战犯听到佛的教诲，让他们理解因果等佛要传达的真理，从而脱离苦海。这里放牌位和一般理解的祭祀之类的意义还真不一样。", "timestamp": 1658677448}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311448, "create_time": 1658678207, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Carol: 万能口袋罪可不是白叫的", "timestamp": 1658678207}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311479, "create_time": 1658678817, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "这人说的解脱好像是为自己解脱吧 她不是噩梦什么的吗", "timestamp": 1658678817}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311499, "create_time": 1658679675, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Grace: 帮助他人解脱和自己解脱是同时的", "timestamp": 1658679675}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311507, "create_time": 1658680225, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "同情", "timestamp": 1658680225}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311538, "create_time": 1658682205, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "既同情她的心理遭遇，也同情她受的不可避免的罚。宗教信仰终究不是脱罪的理由，客观上确实伤害了大部分民众的感情，尤其是有一些南京人，想必痛苦过之而无不及。", "timestamp": 1658682205}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311539, "create_time": 1658682261, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "老英雄唯一的过错就是对支猪太过仁慈了\n[![F2-D4-D699-8523-4-A02-B4-BE-D888-DDF0-EF53.jpg](https://i.postimg.cc/HxjVJwJh/F2-D4-D699-8523-4-A02-B4-BE-D888-DDF0-EF53.jpg)](https://postimg.cc/ftnwp0fc)\n[![22-F01154-3605-44-D2-AEC5-CA75-C55-AAC3-E.jpg](https://i.postimg.cc/q71NMb7K/22-F01154-3605-44-D2-AEC5-CA75-C55-AAC3-E.jpg)](https://postimg.cc/QBW8fq1N)", "timestamp": 1658682261}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311541, "create_time": 1658682318, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "Re Jason: 天火哥速度发条新洞，我看不下去了", "timestamp": 1658682318}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311542, "create_time": 1658682330, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Carol: 这个倒好理解吧。毕竟伤害了民族感情，她知道了就做噩梦，南京人、尤其是幸存的那些人，知道有人这样做，痛苦不得加倍", "timestamp": 1658682330}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311558, "create_time": 1658683822, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Isabella: 伤害民族感情这个后果多少有点虚，她的行为又没有伤害到哪个具体的人的情感，这和侮辱烈士还不一样。而且如果她的供述是真的那幸存者们也应该多少理解她的动机了吧。她只是犯错误，但并不是犯罪。", "timestamp": 1658683822}], "create_time": 1658674609, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1658678817, "likenum": 10, "n_attentions": 10, "n_comments": 16, "pid": 88062, "poll": null, "reply": 16, "text": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/yUzMk7RQnoZb3348iTqpmA\n\n吴啊萍已被刑拘！", "timestamp": 1658674609}}